original: Freidenfelt, Gustaf (Gösta) Fredrik, ingenjör, platschef, Svängsta, f. 6/6/93 i Sthllm av ing. E. F. o. Axelina Heur-lin. G. 27 m. Olga Andersson. Barn: Birgit f. 27, Bertil 31, Kerstin 36. — Realex. i Amål 09, Borås tekn. elem:sk. 14. Anst. h. STAL i Finspång 16-18, Gbgs gasverk 18-19, A-B Original-Odhner 19-28, Halda A-B i Svängsta sed. 28, num. piLatschef där. Medl. av Odd Fellow^. Hobbies: fiske, smalfilmning.
translated: Freidenfelt, Gustaf (Gösta) Fredrik, engineer, site manager, Svängsta, born June 6, 1893 in Stockholm to engineer E.F. and Axelina Heurlin. Married to Olga Andersson in 1927. Children: Birgit born in 1927, Bertil born in 1931, and Kerstin born in 1936. Educated at Realexamen in Amål in 1909 and Borås Technical High School in 1914. Worked at STAL in Finspång from 1916 to 1918, Gbgs gasverk from 1918 to 1919, A-B Original-Odhner from 1919 to 1928. Employed by Halda A-B in Svängsta since 1928, currently holding the position of site manager. Member of Odd Fellows. Hobbies include fishing and amateur filmmaking.
